00:16:01,029 --> 00:16:02,728
Maaf, Sonoko.

262
00:16:02,729 --> 00:16:05,428
Sepertinya aku telah diculik.

263
00:16:05,429 --> 00:16:07,128
Kau diculik?

264
00:16:07,129 --> 00:16:09,029
